tbtc_testimonials.post_content: I also enjoyed hydro therapy for the first time. I learned that there is a difference between being sick and having to resort with lots of water in order go on vacation; people who suffer from severe dehydration could do it at any hour, without leaving their homes or even getting out of bed as we were going around town by foot.

I enjoyed aroma therapy and they were really helpful, but I will recommend just getting a cup of tea or coffee before doing any treatments as you won't be able to identify the correct odor without going down into your nostrils.
